017package org.parboiled.matchers;
018
019import static org.parboiled.common.Preconditions.*;
020import org.parboiled.MatcherContext;
021import org.parboiled.matchervisitors.MatcherVisitor;
022
023/**
024 * A {@link org.parboiled.matchers.Matcher} that never matches anything.
025 */
026public class NothingMatcher extends AbstractMatcher {
027
028    public NothingMatcher() {
029        super("NOTHING");
030    }
031
032    public boolean match(MatcherContext context) {
033        return false;
034    }
035
036    public <R> R accept(MatcherVisitor<R> visitor) {
037        checkArgNotNull(visitor, "visitor");
038        return visitor.visit(this);
039    }
040}
